==Personnel==
;Pink Floyd
*Syd Barrett – guitars, lead vocals on British version of &quot;Astronomy Domine&quot;, &quot;Lucifer Sam&quot;, &quot;Matilda Mother&quot;, &quot;Flaming&quot;, &quot;Pow R. Toc H.&quot;, &quot;The Gnome&quot;, &quot;Chapter 24&quot;, &quot;The Scarecrow&quot;, &quot;Bike&quot;, and &quot;Jugband Blues&quot;
