*** Richard Gomer Berry, 3rd Viscount Kemsley (born 1951)
**** (1) &quot;Hon.&quot; Luke Gomer Berry (born 1998)
**** (2) &quot; Hon.&quot; Jessamine Eleanor Berry (born 1999)
** &quot;Hon. Sir Anthony George Berry (1925–1984)&quot;
